result.name: Cafe Ocean

reviews.text: Very good atmosphere. The service was fast and efficient. We ordered soup and it was delicious.
Food was extremely sub par and overpriced, small portions and not very flavoured.

Great view, overprice, below average food and beverage - in two words: Nothing special. I think it's common for an amusement park. No outside food allowed on the ocean park though and this park was design for people to spend a day here. My advise, have breakfast before come here and basically have lunch for to cure hungry, don't expect too much. Btw, so many shop and few attraction still close when we are here, we arrived 10.30am and the park open at 10.00am.
Can’t use bday buy one get one on rather cheap noodles but expensive dishes
A good place to take a rest and food
